cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.DC, cs.CYBER, cs.SE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on a cloud-based system for state estimation in distribution networks, which involves communication networks and data transmission. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper discusses the implementation of local logic for data transmission and the state estimation system involves monitoring and controlling the distribution network. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is another possible category as the paper deals with a distributed system for state estimation. 
- cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy) is a possible category as the paper may involve security considerations for the IoT cloud-based system. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the software design and implementation of the state estimation system.
